---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="SubSentry — Privacy Policy" description="SubSentry privacy policy. Your data stays on your device.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <!-- Back link + header -->
    <a href="/subsentry" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white text-sm transition mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
      ← Back to SubSentry
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/30 mb-10">Last updated: March 6, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">SubSentry ("the App") is built by Justin Bundrick. This policy explains how your information is handled when you use SubSentry.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white/90">Account information:</strong> When you sign in with Apple, Google, or email, we receive your name and email address solely to create your account. If you use Sign in with Apple's email relay, we only see the relay address.</p>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white/90">Subscription data:</strong> The subscriptions you add — names, amounts, dates, categories — are stored <strong class="text-white/90">locally on your device</strong> and optionally synced via Apple's iCloud (CloudKit) to your other devices.</p>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white/90">Email import (optional):</strong> If you use the AI email import feature, you paste or forward subscription-related emails into the app. The text is processed to extract subscription details. We do not store, read, or retain the email content after parsing.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Bank credentials, credit card numbers, or financial account logins</li>
      <li>Browsing history or location data</li>
      <li>Usage analytics or advertising identifiers</li>
      <li>Contacts, photos, or other personal files</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">All subscription data is stored locally on your device using Apple's secure storage. If you enable iCloud sync, data is stored in your personal iCloud account under Apple's privacy and encryption standards. We do not operate external servers that store your data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">Apple</strong> (Sign in with Apple, iCloud, StoreKit) — subject to <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">Apple's Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">Google</strong> (Google Sign-In) — subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. We only request basic profile info.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">In-App Purchases</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Purchases are processed entirely through Apple's App Store. We do not collect or have access to your payment information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">SubSentry is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">You can delete all your data at any time by deleting the app and disabling iCloud sync. To request account deletion, contact us at the email below.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Changes</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:bunjisolutions@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">bunjisolutions@gmail.com</a></p>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 mt-12 pt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm">
        <a href="/subsentry" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white transition">SubSentry</a>
        <span class="mx-3 text-white/15">·</span>
        <a href="/subsentry/terms-of-service" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white transition">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
